foreignObject.div: ​该资源文件最后一次更改时间，以秒为单位

foreignObject.div: ​方式：Etag是对资源的一种唯一标识，而Last-Modified是该资源文件最后一次更改时间

div.style: outline: none; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; font-size: 12px; font-weight: normal; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, "PingFang SC"; max-width: 480px; min-width: 8px; min-height: 16px; line-height: 1.74; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(70, 70, 70);

foreignObject.div: ​精确度：Etag精确度要优于Last-Modified。因为一秒变化多次Last-Modified监测不到，负责均衡的服务器生成的Last-Modified也不一样

div.style: outline: none; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; font-size: 12px; font-weight: normal; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, "PingFang SC"; max-width: 480px; min-width: 8px; min-height: 16px; line-height: 1.74; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(70, 70, 70);

foreignObject.div: ​性能：Etag要逊于Last-Modified，毕竟Last-Modified只需要记录时间，而Etag需要服务器通过算法来计算出一个hash值。

div.style: outline: none; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; font-size: 12px; font-weight: normal; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, "PingFang SC"; max-width: 480px; min-width: 8px; min-height: 16px; line-height: 1.74; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(70, 70, 70);

foreignObject.div: ​优先级：服务器校验优先考虑Etag。

div.style: outline: none; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; font-size: 12px; font-weight: normal; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, "PingFang SC"; max-width: 480px; min-width: 8px; min-height: 16px; line-height: 1.74; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(70, 70, 70);

foreignObject.div: ​先比较当前时间和上一次返回200时的时间差，如果没有超过cache-control设置的max-age，则没有过期，命中强缓存

div.style: outline: none; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; font-size: 12px; font-weight: normal; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, "PingFang SC"; max-width: 480px; min-width: 8px; min-height: 16px; line-height: 1.74; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(70, 70, 70);

foreignObject.div: 如果时间过期，则向服务器发送header带有If-None-Match和If-Modified-Since的请求；

div.style: outline: none; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; font-size: 12px; font-weight: normal; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, "PingFang SC"; max-width: 480px; min-width: 8px; min-height: 16px; line-height: 1.74; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(70, 70, 70);

foreignObject.div: ​服务器收到请求后，优先根据Etag的值判断被请求的文件有没有做修改，Etag值一致则没有修改，命中协商缓存，返回304；如果不一致则有改动，直接返回新的资源文件带上新的Etag值并返回200；若无ETag则则将If-Modified-Since和被请求文件的最后修改时间做比对，一致则命中协商缓存，返回304；不一致则返回新的last-modified和文件并返回200；

foreignObject.div: ​地址栏访问，链接跳转是正常用户行为，将会触发浏览器缓存机制；

div.style: outline: none; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; font-size: 12px; font-weight: normal; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, "PingFang SC"; max-width: 480px; min-width: 8px; min-height: 16px; line-height: 1.74; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(70, 70, 70);

foreignObject.div: ​F5刷新，浏览器会设置max-age=0，跳过强缓存判断，会进行协商缓存判断；

div.style: outline: none; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; font-size: 12px; font-weight: normal; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, "PingFang SC"; max-width: 480px; min-width: 8px; min-height: 16px; line-height: 1.74; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(70, 70, 70);

foreignObject.div: ​ctrl+F5刷新，跳过强缓存和协商缓存，直接从服务器拉取资源。
